<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 03:20:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本向中方转达对台湾周边军演的关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-conveys-china-its-concern-over-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-10-15/</link><description>日本官房副长官青木和彦在例行记者会上表示，日本已向中国表达了对周一在台湾周边进行的军事演习的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 03:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-conveys-china-its-concern-over-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-10-15/</guid></item><item><title>台湾详细介绍参与军演的中国战机数量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-details-record-surge-chinese-warplanes-involved-war-games-2024-10-15/</link><description>台湾国防部周二详细介绍了前一天军演期间中国战机在台湾周边活动激增的情况，称其发现了创纪录的 153 架中国军用飞机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 02:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-details-record-surge-chinese-warplanes-involved-war-games-2024-10-15/</guid></item><item><title>大多数亚洲股市跟随华尔街走高，石油扩大跌幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-15/</link><description>周二，受华尔街股市强劲收盘和投资者对企业盈利的乐观情绪支撑，亚洲股市大多走高，而美元则在下个月美国降息幅度较小的押注的推动下，维持在两个月高点附近。</description><pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 02:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商远洋集团预计将产生28亿美元现金来偿还海外债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-developer-sino-ocean-expects-generate-28-bln-cash-repay-offshore-debt-2024-10-15/</link><description>中国房地产开发商远洋集团周二表示，重组计划正在有序实施，预计未来十年将产生28亿美元现金，用于偿还新的融资工具。</description><pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 00:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-developer-sino-ocean-expects-generate-28-bln-cash-repay-offshore-debt-2024-10-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国表现强劲，欧洲复苏，9月全球电动汽车销量增长30.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-305-september-china-shines-europe-recuperates-2024-10-14/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 周二表示，9 月份全球纯电动和插电式混合动力汽车销量同比增长 30.5%，其中中国超过了 8 月份创下的纪录，欧洲也恢复了增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:04:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-305-september-china-shines-europe-recuperates-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：东京重新开市，标准普尔 500 指数创历史新高，人民币下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-14/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 21:49:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis董事长埃尔坎：对收购竞争对手不感兴趣 - 法新社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chair-elkann-not-interested-buying-competitors-afp-2024-10-14/</link><description>这家法国-意大利汽车制造商董事长约翰·埃尔坎 (John Elkann) 周一对法新社表示，近期有传言称 Stellantis 与法国竞争对手雷诺 (Renault) 合作，因此并不寻求与其他公司合并或收购其他公司。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 19:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chair-elkann-not-interested-buying-competitors-afp-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>英国呼吁中国在台湾周边军演后保持克制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-calls-restraint-after-chinas-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-10-14/</link><description>英国周一表示，对中国在台湾周边进行的军事演习感到担忧，并表示这些演习加剧了紧张局势，并有可能导致台海局势“危险升级”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 19:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-calls-restraint-after-chinas-military-drills-around-taiwan-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼猛烈抨击中国在台湾周边进行的军演“破坏稳定”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pentagon-slams-destabilizing-chinese-war-games-around-taiwan-2024-10-14/</link><description>五角大楼周一强烈批评中国在台湾周围进行军事演习，称其破坏稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:55:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pentagon-slams-destabilizing-chinese-war-games-around-taiwan-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>英国没有计划对中国电动汽车征收欧盟式的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/britain-has-no-plans-eu-style-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-10-14/</link><description>英国贸易大臣乔纳森·雷诺兹周一表示，英国不打算效仿欧盟对从中国进口的电动汽车征收关税，因为英国企业尚未提出投诉接受调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 16:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/britain-has-no-plans-eu-style-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟官员称中国电动汽车价格在10月底前很难达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hard-see-chinese-ev-price-deal-by-end-october-says-eu-official-2024-10-14/</link><description>一位欧盟高级官员表示，欧盟与北京就最低进口价格进行谈判，以避免欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，这是一个“巨大的挑战”，因为汽车是复杂的产品，而且报价必须充分且可执行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 14:38:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hard-see-chinese-ev-price-deal-by-end-october-says-eu-official-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟“希望公平竞争”，但仍在与中国就汽车关税进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-wants-level-playing-field-still-negotiating-with-china-car-tariffs-2024-10-14/</link><description>欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩周一表示，欧盟希望在汽车关税问题上与中国建立公平的竞争环境，并正在与北京就价格承诺或欧洲投资等机制进行谈判，以作为解决方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 14:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-wants-level-playing-field-still-negotiating-with-china-car-tariffs-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>塔瓦雷斯表示，欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税将加速欧洲工厂关闭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-accelerate-plant-closures-europe-tavares-says-2024-10-14/</link><description>Stellantis首席执行官周一表示，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税将加速当地汽车制造商关闭欧洲工厂，因为关税将推动中国制造商在欧洲建设工厂，从而加剧产能过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 13:59:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-evs-accelerate-plant-closures-europe-tavares-says-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，汇丰银行就中国顶峰财富业务的成本和控制问题展开调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-probes-china-pinnacle-wealth-business-costs-control-say-sources-2024-10-14/</link><description>多位消息人士称，汇丰控股正在审查其中国数字财富业务 Pinnacle 的费用和运营控制，此举可能导致裁员，并标志着该银行对该部门雄心的突然逆转。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 12:54:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-probes-china-pinnacle-wealth-business-costs-control-say-sources-2024-10-14/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪要求欧盟在扩大欧洲供应链时“远离”关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-warns-eu-tariffs-will-raise-prices-deter-buyers-2024-10-14/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周一猛烈抨击了欧盟计划对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，但表示计划在欧洲销售的几乎所有汽车都在本地生产，加入了一系列中国汽车制造商加速在该地区生产计划的行列。</description><pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-warns-eu-tariffs-will-raise-prices-deter-buyers-2024-10-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>